The Great American Coffee Taste Test data

coffee_survey.Rd

The data comes from the "Great American Coffee Taste Test" conducted by James Hoffmann and Cometeer in October 2023. Survey ...

Usage

coffee_survey

Format

A data frame with 4,042 rows and 6 columns:

prefer_overall

Respondent's preferred coffee type

gender

Respondent's gender

age

Respondent's age group

where_drink

Typical location where coffee is consumed

brew

Coffee brewing method used

most_paid

Respondent's age group

...
